  <section id="guide-preface-intro">
   <title>Introduction</title>

   <para>This guide to <application>PyPop</application> contains is in
    three parts:</para>

   <itemizedlist>
    <listitem>
     <para><xref linkend="guide-chapter-install"/>
      describes how to install the application either using a
      standalone binary version that you can simply download and
      install, or for programmers and other interested parties there
      is a source version which you can build the application
      yourself</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
     <para><xref linkend="guide-chapter-usage"/>
      which describes how run <application>PyPop</application>.</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
     <para><xref linkend="guide-chapter-instructions"/> which details
      the population genetics methods and statistics that
      <application>PyPop</application> performs.</para>

    </listitem>
